title: Genasi of Water
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki
xpcost: 1

As a water [[genasi]], you gain the following benefits.

* You have resistance to [[acid damage|damage type]].
* You can breathe air and water, and can swim as fast as you can run.
* You can cast one of the following spells: [[shape water]], [[create or destroy water]], [[acid splash]], [[ray of frost]], [[water walk]], or [[ice knife]].